settings.title: Important Information
settings.content:
Sleepytroll Bed Rocker Feet comes with 4 screws (pre-drilling required) and can only be mounted on cribs wit wooden legs.

Maximum weight of the crib itself should not exceed 48.5 lbs (excluding bedding, mattress, and baby) to facilitate a proper rocking motion, and to not put unneccesary strain on the Sleepytroll motor.Â 

We do not recommend using the Bed Rocker Feet on the crib once your baby can stand (risk of tipping).
